{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some of them, their wound was rotting already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There, but they were jammed out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "All this was one-- one huge basement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were on the floor, on the spread out-- spread out straw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were blankets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were all these children there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could imagine, you see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And food, whoever they could get to get it and steal food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and smuggled it-- smuggled that in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they collected most of-- of these children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have a book.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it's in-- in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So mostly-- mostly woman charity organization, religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Including Catholic woman's organization.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] herself was the-- was the-- the chair of the-- of the-- Cattolica.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The woman's branch of the Cattolica.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there's this-- the woman's organization, national woman's organization of the-- of the Catholic-- Catholic woman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was the national chairman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so she-- she helped in-- where were they-- that they took-- took them-- took them into monasteries and-- and many, many other places.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- I-- I have some in the book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But and they trade union [NON-ENGLISH] and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where-- the-- the parents were-- were driven away, into-- into the-- into yellow cross-- yellow star houses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't [NON-ENGLISH] house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was the yellow star houses where-- where they ghettoed them all around.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or-- or drove them away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the [NON-ENGLISH] people, men and-- men and women into the German underground, underground factories, war factories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- and the children's were left behind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there-- there were people who gathered them, all-- all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they took-- took care of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the church basement, or the church, or the schools, and trade union halls and such organizations.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
